													<div class="avatar"><img class="avatar" src="images/avatars/noavatar.gif" alt="" /></div>												<p><img src="images/2008/star_level1.gif" alt="Rank: 4" /><img src="images/2008/star_level1.gif" alt="Rank: 4" /><img src="images/2008/star_level1.gif" alt="Rank: 4" /><img src="images/2008/star_level1.gif" alt="Rank: 4" /></p>
                        
